\par\pard\plain \tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 Here\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s the elevator speech:  Offer rewards for a rich set of less-social and less-creative behaviors that the players already }{\f2\fs26\b0\i1\cf1 want}{\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1  to do.  }
