\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 - watch shows, listen to music}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 - explore}
\par\plain \f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 Seek to align rewards to intrinsic desires and provide a path towards the fully intrinsically-motivated behaviors.  }
