\par\plain \f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 The negative outcome the be avoided is }{\f0\fs26\b1\i0\cf1 player\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s remorse}{\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 .  This is the drug addiction feeling.  A player (or reader) has been }{\f2\fs26\b0\i1\cf1 motivated, but not fulfilled}{\f1\fs26\b0\i0\cf1  and this realization gets worse over time. }
